text: Adelaide United F.C. is a soccer club from Adelaide, South Australia, Australia. It competes in the A-League, under licence from Football Federation Australia (FFA). Adelaide United were the first A-League premiers. ==Honours== *A-League :Premiers (1): 2005–06 :Runners-up (2): 2006–07, 2008–09 *A-League Finals :Runners-up (2): 2007, 2009 *AFC Champions League :Runners-up (1): 2008 ==References== Category:A-League Men Category:2003 establishments in Australia
title: Adelaide United FC
